data.description: Looking for that great move in ready home this one has so much to offer.  This is a four bedroom 2 bath with detached garage.  This home is move in ready with all new interior paint, new carpet, new AC unit, new led lighting, new blinds, and much more.   Great back yard for entertaining friends, family, or just hanging out. Mature tree in the front with a covered patio just waiting on your chairs to enjoy.  I cant wait for you to see this one lets get you packed and moved.
